# =============================================================================
# Bindings — reconcile Worker UI vs wrangler.production.toml (resource IDs stay in toml)
# =============================================================================
# AI (Workers AI)
# AI_SEARCH (Workers AI Search / ai_search in toml)
# ASSETS            -> R2 inneranimalmedia-assets
# CAD_ASSETS        -> R2 splineicons
# CHESS_SESSION     -> Durable Object ChessRoom
# DASHBOARD         -> R2 agent-sam
# DB                -> D1 inneranimalmedia-business
# HYPERDRIVE        -> Hyperdrive inneranimalmedia-supabase-hyperdrive
# IAM_COLLAB        -> Durable Object IAMCollaborationSession
# KV                -> KV MCP_TOKENS
# MYBROWSER         -> Browser Rendering
# MY_QUEUE          -> Queue (producer + consumer; ID in toml only)
# R2                -> R2 iam-platform
# SESSION_CACHE     -> KV production-KV_SESSIONS
# VECTORIZE         -> Vectorize ai-search-inneranimalmedia-aisearch
# VECTORIZE_INDEX   -> Vectorize ai-search-iam-autorag
# WAE               -> Analytics Engine dataset inneranimalmedia

# =============================================================================
# Cron triggers — must match wrangler.production.toml [triggers].crons and dashboard
# =============================================================================
# */30 * * * *
# 0 0 * * *
# 30 13 * * *
# 0 6 * * *
# 0 9 * * *

# =============================================================================
# Routes / domains (sanity check vs dashboard)
# =============================================================================
# inneranimalmedia.com/*   www.inneranimalmedia.com/*   webhooks.inneranimalmedia.com/*
# workers.dev + preview URLs as configured for project inneranimalmedia
